messages.message:
Hey team,

For any excel file uploaded, we are not able to see ocr text output from the UI. This hinders us from analysing the ocr engine's output.

this has never been a feature

can you submit a feature request for this?
@Serena This is something we had in our classic platform.

@Abhishek Adupa did we have re-extraction in the classic platform?

based on the docs (https://platform.instabase.com/docs/review-results/document-reviewer-guide/index.html), my understanding is that the fields will all have empty values after the class label is modified -> the user needs to manually add the field values

> did we have re-extraction in the classic platform?
No, you are right - user had to fill them manually (afaik)
